snippet.title: CODE VEIN - Successor of the Ribcage Boss Trailer | X1, PS4, PC
snippet.description:
Don't let chains tie down your humanity in CODE VEIN! Prepare for a ruff battle against the Successor of the Ribcage!

Pre-Order #CODEVEIN now and team up with fellow revenants starting September 27th: https://bandainam.co/codevein
